{"tid":1739170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[科學台] 用酒精做燃料好危險","createTime":"2019-11-19T13:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T11:21:36.000Z","uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8fd06f33bdd7af1823cee30e3627cef0d7c5f9b","tid":1739170,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cl86p3ZjuSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dcl86p3ZjuSM&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=114bde5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cl86p3ZjuSM</a><br />\n<br />\n加燃料既時候要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b61bbc6a266af697dfcf7c02ea1aa587d1c05b2","tid":1739170,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:28:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190924002997-260405?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190924002997-260405%3Fchdtv&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=b4a8a685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190924002997-260405?chdtv</a><br />\n<br />\n《佑來了》研判，兩女童應該是尚未熄滅酒精燈上的火源就擅自打開蓋子，在灌油時產生強烈氣爆，而溢出的酒精液體沾黏在女童身上，由於屬液態，根本撲滅不了，只能任由酒精燃燒殆盡，造成難以挽回的悲慘局面。<br />\n<br />\n在他影片中，他分享國外酒精燃燒產生氣爆的實驗，顯示出酒精燈引爆的「威力」多麼驚人！當氣態酒精瞬間燃燒，位於瓶口的正前方的人根本無處可逃，實在可怕。因此《佑來了》不斷呼籲使用酒精燈要非常小心，沒加熱時務必要將火給確實熄滅，以免再度發生憾事。"},{"pid":"4023d7526981a4bda4343e70b3229e89e7677df1","tid":1739170,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75012816942663b36b44f0c0609cc794bf95f75","tid":1739170,"uid":100871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4023d7526981a4bda4343e70b3229e89e7677df1","tid":1739170,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"